---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle="Privacy" bodyClass="login">

<style>
    body.login {
        align-items: stretch;
        justify-content: flex-start;
    }

    body.login > h1,
    body.login > h2,
    body.login > p,
    body.login > ul {
        max-width: 720px;
        width: 100%;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        padding-left: 1rem;
        padding-right: 1rem;
        text-align: left;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
</style>

<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Last Updated: May 6, 2026</p>

        <p>This Privacy Policy describes how <strong>Site Activity Log Viewer</strong> ("we," "us," or "our") handles your information. Our commitment to your privacy is simple: we only use the data necessary to provide the service and we do not store your information.</p>

        <h2>1. Information Collection and Access</h2>
        <p>Our tool operates as a real-time viewer and does not maintain a permanent database of your activity logs. Information is handled as follows:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>OAuth Authentication:</strong> You log in using an external provider. We receive an authentication token to access your data, but we never see or store your password.</li>
            <li><strong>Data Retrieval:</strong> We fetch your site activity logs via API for the sole purpose of displaying them to you. This data is processed in-memory and is not saved to our servers.</li>
            <li><strong>Temporary Cookies:</strong> We use temporary session cookies strictly to manage your authenticated session. These are deleted when you log out or close your browser.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. Data Storage and Retention</h2>
        <p>We do not store, archive, or retain any of the log data retrieved through the application. Once your session is closed, the data is gone from our systems.</p>

        <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information or log data to outside parties. Your data is never reused for any purpose other than providing the immediate "Viewer" service.</p>

        <h2>4. Security</h2>
        <p>We utilize industry-standard OAuth protocols to ensure secure access to your data without requiring your account credentials. We recommend logging out of the application when your session is complete.</p>

        <h2>5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>Any updates to this policy will be reflected on this page with an updated "Last Updated" date.</p>

        <h2>6. Contact</h2>
        <p>For questions regarding this policy, please email raymond.camden@webflow.com.</p>

</BaseLayout>